30
00:01:38,230 --> 00:01:43,770
rather our students learn when they take
our words and apply them to lab,

31
00:01:43,770 --> 00:01:50,300
designing, developing, testing,
evaluating, on a real lab environment.

32
00:01:50,300 --> 00:01:54,440
